# game/script/chapter2.rpy:28
translate english c02_0000:

    # c "던전은 서로 다른 공간을 강제로 이어 붙인 것처럼 기묘한 조화를 이루는 공간이다."
    c base out_d "Dungeons are spaces exhibiting a strange harmony, as if two different areas have been forcefully melded together."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:30
translate english c02_0001:

    # c "벽에는 각양각색의 곰팡이가 얼룩덜룩하게 피어있고, 마나를 머금고 희미하게 빛나는 이끼가 불규칙한 패턴으로 성장하고 있었다."
    c "The walls were speckled with fungi of all shapes and hues, and growing over them in irregular patterns were moss that glowed faintly with the mana it held within."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:32
translate english c02_0002:

    # c "마물의 흔적이나 다른 사람의 야영 흔적 같은 것도 가끔씩 남아있다. 던전이 그냥 동굴과 다른 점은 마력에 따라 움직이는 것이다."
    c "There are also the occasional traces of monsters and the remnants of other adventurers' campsites. What makes a dungeon different from a cave is that mana sets it in motion."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:34
translate english c02_0003:

    # c "던전 그 자체가 살아 숨 쉬고 있다. 매 순간 공간이 조금씩 변화하고, 벽의 일부는 마치 살아서 꿈틀거리는 듯했다."
    c "The dungeon itself breathes as if it's a living animal. Not a moment goes by without the space shifting slightly, and parts of the wall seem to come alive and squirm."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:44
translate english c02_0004:

    # c "나와 가헬은 조심스럽게 걸어가며, 이 기괴한 풍경을 조용히 감상했다."
    c out_d "Gahel and I walked cautiously, quietly registering this bizarre landscape."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:46
translate english c02_0005:

    # c "\"항상 느끼는 거지만, 던전 내부는 정말 기묘해... 마치 여러 조직을 이어 붙인 생물의 내장에 들어온 느낌이야.\""
    c talk "\"I always say this, but the dungeon's interior is a strange, strange place... It's like crawing into the intestines of a creature stitched together from multiple organs.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:48
translate english c02_0006:

    # "가헬은 [pl_name]의 말에 대해 잠시 생각에 잠긴 듯하더니, 무겁게 대답했다."
    "Gahel seemed to ponder [pl_name]'s words for a moment, then replied solemnly."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:55
translate english c02_0007:

    # w "\"내장이라... 끔찍한 비유지만, 부정할 수는 없겠군.\""
    w "\"Intestines, you say... A horrid analogy, but an undeniable one.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:60
translate english c02_0008:

    # c "우리는 마나 허브를 찾기 위해 발걸음을 재촉했다."
    c base "We quickened our pace on our pursuit of a mana herb."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:62
translate english c02_0009:

    # c "가능한 넓은 범위를 탐지하기 위해 던전의 중간쯤까지 가야 했다. 지도를 따라 공터에 도달하자, 나는 공간탐지 마법을 준비했다."
    c "We had to travel roughly halfway into the dungeon to scan as much ground as possible. Upon following the map and reaching a clearing, I prepared the spatial detection spell."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:64
translate english c02_0010:

    # "[pl_name]의 몸에서 서서히 피어오르는 푸른 빛무리가 어둠을 밀어내며 신비로운 광채를 발산했다."
    "A cluster of blue light slowly emanated from [pl_name]'s body, repelling the darkness and exuding a mysterious radiance."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:71
translate english c02_0011:

    # c "이 마력은 내 발끝에서 시작해 물줄기를 타고 흐르는 나뭇잎처럼 하늘거리며, 끊임없이 변화하는 던전의 깊숙한 곳까지 스며들었다."
    c "This mana stirred at my feet and fluttered like a leaf floating down a stream before seeping into the ever-changing depths of the dungeon."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:73
translate english c02_0012:

    # c "주변을 경계하는 가헬과 주문을 사용하는 내 숨소리 외에는 숨죽은 듯 고요했지만, 빛나는 마력의 실을 통해 느껴지는 던전은 꽉 찬 술집처럼 시끄러웠다."
    c "Although the place kept silent as if holding its breath minus the sound of my breathing and Gahel warding our surroundings, the dungeon I felt through the strands of mana felt as riotous as inside of a crowded tavern."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:75
translate english c02_0013:

    # c "나는 손에 든 지도와 탐지 마법을 통해 느껴지는 던전을 비교하며 가헬에게 말했다."
    c "Cross-examining the dungeon pictured on the map in my hand and the dungeon I felt through the detection magic, I spoke to Gahel."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:77
translate english c02_0014:

    # c "\"음, 일단 문제 없어. 지도와 거의 다르지 않네. 동쪽에 샘, 서쪽에 마물로 막힌 통로도 그대로야. 마나 허브는... 북서쪽에 있어.\""
    c talk "\"Hmm, it looks like we've got this. It's just as the map says. The fountain is to the East, and the monster-ridden path really is to the West too. The mana herbs... are in the Northwest.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:79
translate english c02_0015:

    # c "말을 마치자마자, 나는 던전의 지도를 접어 주머니에 넣었다. 가헬은 말없이 주변을 경계하던 중, 고개를 끄덕였다."
    c base "As soon as I finished speaking, I folded the map of the dungeon and tucked it in my pocket. Gahel, who had been silently watching our surroundings, nodded."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:81
translate english c02_0016:

    # c "고요한 던전 길을 따라 걷다가 가헬이 입을 열었다. 아까 사용한 탐지 마법이 궁금한 것 같았다."
    c "Walking along the quiet dungeon path, Gahel spoke up, seemingly curious about the detection magic I had used earlier."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:86
translate english c02_0017:

    # w "\"탐지 마법으로 다양한 정보를 추적할 수 있는 마법사는 드문 걸로 알고 있는데, 대단하군.\""
    w "\"I heard mages who can trace various pieces of information with detection magic are hard to come by. That was impressive.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:91
translate english c02_0018:

    # c "\"전에 던전 탐사 때도 보여줬잖아. 새삼스럽게 왜?\""
    c talk "\"You've seen me do it last time we went dungeon diving. Any reason you bring it up now?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:96
translate english c02_0019:

    # w "\"그때는 단순한 표면을 추적하는 마법으로만 생각했지.\""
    w "\"Back then, I supposed it was just a elementary surface-tracking spell.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:98
translate english c02_0020:

    # w "\"대부분 마법사들은 공간 전체를 파악하려면 너무 많은 정보에 압도되기 때문에, 특정 대상만 추적하는 편이라고 들었다.\""
    w "\"I've been told most mages are able to track only a specific target because the sheer amount of information that comes with understanding the entirety of a space can be overwhelming.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:103
translate english c02_0021:

    # "그가 신기하다는 듯 이어 말했다."
    "He continued, seemingly intrigued."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:108
translate english c02_0022:

    # w "\"너도 그렇게 마나 허브를 추적하는 줄 알았는데, 던전에서 탐지 마법으로 정확히 공간 정보를 읽어내다니. 흔한 마법사와는 다르군.\""
    w "\"I thought you were tracking just the mana herbs, but you were precisely reading the spatial information of the entire dungeon with a detection spell. I now see that you're no ordinary mage.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:113
translate english c02_0023:

    # "[pl_name][josa_eun_neun] 살짝 민망한 웃음을 지으며 대답했다."
    "[pl_name], with a slightly embarrassed smile, responded."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:115
translate english c02_0024:

    # c "\"하하, 용병 마법사면 아무래도 전투용 원소 마법이 특기일 테니까.\""
    c smile "\"Haha, it's only natural that a mercenary mage would specialize in combative elemental magic, after all.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:117
translate english c02_0025:

    # c "\"마탑의 정식 마법사에게 이런 건 아무것도 아닐 거야. 성도 반대편에서 잃어버린 동전도 찾을 수 있을걸?\""
    c talk "\"I bet the official mages of the Magic Tower could do the same without breaking a sweat. They could probably find a lost coin on the other side of the city.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:119
translate english c02_0026:

    # "가헬은 여전히 [pl_name][josa_eul_reul] 대단하다고 생각하는 듯 빛나는 눈이었다."
    "Gahel's eyes still shone, seemingly thinking [pl_name] was remarkable."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:124
translate english c02_0027:

    # w "\"회복 물약에 마탑 공증을 받은 것도 그렇고, 혹시 마탑에서 교육을 받았어?\""
    w "\"You got the Magic Tower's notary for your healing potions too. Did you receive training at the Magic Tower?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:129
translate english c02_0028:

    # c "\"그랬으면 계약할 때 신분 증명이 상인이 아니라 마법사였을걸?\""
    c talk "\"If that were the case, the proof of identity I submitted when we singed our contract would have said I was a mage, not a merchant, right?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:131
translate english c02_0029:

    # c "\"마탑에 들어가려면 엄청난 경쟁률을 자랑하는 시험에 합격부터 해야 하고, 거기서 정식 마법사가 되기까지 어마어마한 돈이 든다고.\""
    c "\"If I were to enter the Magic Tower, I'd have to pass a highly competitive exam, and only from then onwards will the tremendous amount of money I'd need to become a formal mage become a problem.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:133
translate english c02_0030:

    # c "\"난 그렇게 재능이 있지도, 돈이 많지도 않아서... 회복 물약은 마탑의 지인을 통해 인증받은 거야.\""
    c "\"I neither have that much talent nor money... I got the healing potion notarized with the help of an acquaintance at the Magic Tower.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:135
translate english c02_0031:

    # "[pl_name]의 대답에 가헬은 의문을 표했다."
    "Gahel expressed doubt at [pl_name]'s answer."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:140
translate english c02_0032:

    # w "\"그럼, 마법은 어떻게 배운 거야?\""
    w "\"Then, how did you learn magic?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:145
translate english c02_0033:

    # c "\"어릴 때 스승님이 있었거든. 특이한 용 수인이었어.\""
    c talk "\"I had a master when I was young. He was quite the eccentric dragon beastman.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:147
translate english c02_0034:

    # "가헬은 잠시 놀라서 [pl_name][josa_eul_reul] 바라봤다."
    "Gahel looked at [pl_name] in surprise for a moment."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:149
translate english c02_0035:

    # w "(단 한 명의 스승에게?... 스승이 뛰어난 건가, 아니면...)"
    w "(From just one master…? Was it the master who's extraordinary, or...)"
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:154
translate english c02_0036:

    # w "\"...그럼 마탑의 지인은?\""
    w "\"...Then, about your acquaintance at the Magic Tower?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:159
translate english c02_0037:

    # c "\"아, 음. '바토'라고 있어. 걔한테 배운 건 아냐. 상점을 차렸을 때쯤에 처음 만났거든.\""
    c talk "\"Ah, hm. His name is 'Bato'. I didn't learn magic from him. I first met him around the time I opened my shop.\""

# game/script/chapter2.rpy:161
translate english c02_0038:

    # c "나는 가헬과 '바토'라는 곰 수인에 대해 얘기하며 걸어갔다."
    c base "I walked and chatted with Gahel about 'Bato', the bear beastman."

# game/script/chapter2.rpy:163
translate english c02_0039:

    # c "원래 그는 마탑에서 허가받지 않은 {color=#ee3939}'금지된 마법'{/color} 같은 행위를 단속하는 업무를 하는데, 내 상점이 새로 생길 때도 검사를 하기 위해 찾아왔다."
    c "His job at the Magic Tower is policing unlicensed activities like {color=#ee3939}'forbidden magic'{/color}, and he stopped by to inspect my shop when it newly opened."

# game/script/chapter2.rpy:165
translate english c02_0040:

    # c "당연히 내 가게에는 문제가 없었지만, 바토가 쓰러지는 소동이 있었고 그때 도와준 인연으로 마탑 공증 문서까지 받게 되었다."
    c "Naturally, there were no issues with my shop, but there was an incident where Bato suddenly became unconscious, and I received a Magic Tower notary document for helping him."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:174
translate english c02_0041:

    # c "한가로운 수다 시간은 오래가지 않았다. 배회하는 하급 마물 몇을 쓰러뜨리고 마나 허브 군락에 도착했다."
    c out_d "The leisurely chatter didn't last long. After defeating a few wandering low-level monsters, we arrived at a colony of mana herbs."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:176
translate english c02_0042:

    # c "빽빽하게 자라난 초록 수풀은 물약으로 만들어 팔 생각에 침이 꿀꺽 넘어갈 수준으로 가득 자라나 있었다."
    c "The densely flourishing verdure unfurled so lushly that it made one's mouth water at the thought of turning them into profitable potions."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:178
translate english c02_0043:

    # c "물론 전부 채집해 가면 나중에 내가 다시 왔을 때도 자라나지 않을 수 있으니, 적당히 반 정도만 가져가야 한다."
    c "Of course, if I harvested all of them, they might not have grown back the time I return, so I should take only about half."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:180
translate english c02_0044:

    # c "나는 전용 주머니를 꺼내 허브를 채집할 준비를 했다."
    c "I took out a specialized pouch to start harvesting the herbs."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:190
translate english c02_0045:

    # c "\"가헬도 한번 채집해 볼래? 생각보다 쉬워.\""
    c talk "\"Want to try harvesting them, Gahel? It's easier than you think.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:197
translate english c02_0046:

    # w "\"어떻게 하는 건가?\""
    w "\"How do I harvest them?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:202
translate english c02_0047:

    # c "나를 도와주려는 가헬의 앞에서 직접 시범을 보였다."
    c base "I demonstrated in front of Gahel who leaned in to help."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:204
translate english c02_0048:

    # c "\"시들지 않게 뿌리 끝을 마나로 감싸고 줄기가 끊어지지 않게 뽑는 거야. 마력보단 손재주가 중요할걸?\""
    c talk "\"Wrap the root ends with mana to prevent wilting and ensure the stems don't break when you pull. It's more about dexterity than magical affinity.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:209
translate english c02_0049:

    # w "\"그건... 나는 마력을 조작형으로 사용할 수 없다. 시술을 받아서...\""
    w "\"That's... I cannot manipulate mana like that. I've recieved a {color=#ee3939}'procedure'{/color}...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:211
translate english c02_0050:

    # c "\"응? 아... 그렇구나.\""
    c talk "\"Huh? Oh... I see.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:216
translate english c02_0051:

    # c "힘이 전부인 용병의 세상에서 몸에 술식을 새겨넣는 일은 흔하다."
    c base "It's common practice to engrave magical formulas on one's body in the world of a mercenary where physical strength is everything."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:218
translate english c02_0052:

    # c "재능이 있다면 훈련을 통해 검기를 발생시킨다거나 받는 충격을 흘려낸다거나 하는 마법이 가능하지만, 용병이라면 쉽고 빠르게 시술로 해결하는 게 이득일 것이다."
    c "Magic such as materializing sword slashes or deflecting incoming strikes become possible through training if one has the talent"
    
    c "But for a mercenary, it's more efficient to attain them quickly and easily through magical procedures."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:220
translate english c02_0053:

    # c "물론 시술은 만능이 아니다. 아무래도 가헬은 마나를 흡수해서 근육을 강화하는 술식밖에 사용할 수 없는 것 같다."
    c "Of course, such procedures aren't all-powerful. It seems Gahel can only use formulas that absorb mana to strengthen his muscles."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:225
translate english c02_0054:

    # w "\"시간이 꽤 걸릴 테니, 그동안 주변을 지켜보도록 하지.\""
    w "\"This might take some time, so keep an eye on our surroundings for now.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:233
translate english c02_0055:

    # c "\"채집하는 동안 주변을 지켜줄 수 있을까?\""
    c talk "\"Can you watch over the area while I harvest?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:240
translate english c02_0056:

    # w "\"알겠다.\""
    w "\"Understood.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:245
translate english c02_0057:

    # "조용한 던전 안에서 대화마저 끊기니 숨 막히는 침묵이 이어졌다."
    "A suffocating silence followed as even the conversation ceased in the quiet dungeon."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:247
translate english c02_0058:

    # c "(차라리 같이 채집하자고 할 걸 그랬나...)"
    c consider "(Maybe I should have asked him to help with the harvesting after all...)"
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:249
translate english c02_0059:

    # c "나는 어떻게든 수닷거리라도 꺼내볼까 하다가 그냥 채집에 집중했다."
    c base "I thought start some small talk, but decided to just focus on the harvesting."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:251
translate english c02_0060:

    # c "(빨리 끝내는 편이 낫겠다.)"
    c "(I better pick up the pace.)"
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:259
translate english c02_0061:

    # c "\"휴. 이 정도면 충분하겠지?\""
    c out_d "\"Phew. This should be enough, right?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:266
translate english c02_0062:

    # "[pl_name][josa_i_ga] 세심하게 허브를 뜯어 주머니를 가득 채우는 동안, 가헬은 [pl_name][josa_eul_reul] 지켜보다가 가까이 온 박쥐 마물을 베어버리거나 했다."
    "As [pl_name] filled the pouch with carefully-picked herbs, Gahel watched over [pl_name], occasionally slashing at approaching bat monsters."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:271
translate english c02_0063:

