    # w "\"콜로니의 마물이 던전에 유입된 것 같다. 그것도 꽤 많은 수가.\""
    w "\"It appears that the Colony's monsters have entered the dungeon, and quite a few of them.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:900
translate english c02_0215:

    # l "\"자세한 증언 감사합니다. 이 사건은 '반슈타인' 기사단에도 공유해야겠군요.\""
    l "\"Thank you for your detailed testimony. I'll have to share this case with the Knights of 'Bernstein'.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:902
translate english c02_0216:

    # "심하면 던전에서 마물 콜로니가 새로 생길 수도 있다. 물론 그렇게 되면 기사단이 처리하겠지만, 위험한 일은 하나라도 적은 편이 좋다."
    "In the worst case scenario, a new monster colony might spawn in the dungeon. The Knights will take care of that, of course, but it's better to take fewer risks."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:906
translate english c02_0217:

    # "가헬과 증언을 마치고 가게로 돌아오는 길에 고기를 크게 한 덩이 샀다. 육체의 부상은 치료했으나 정신적인 휴식이 필요할 것이다."
    "On his way back to the shop after his testimony with Gahel, [pl_name] bought a large cut of meat. Gahel's physical injuries were healed, but he will need mental rest."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:908
translate english c02_0218:

    # c "\"오늘은 든든하게 먹고, 내일 영업도 혼자 할 테니 푹 쉬어.\""
    c talk "\"Eat well today, and get a good night's sleep because you'll be running the business tomorrow.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:913
translate english c02_0219:

    # "가헬은 [pl_name][josa_eul_reul] 물끄러미 바라보다가 활짝 웃었다."
    "Gahel looked at [pl_name] and smiled broadly."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:918
translate english c02_0220:

    # w "\"고마워.\""
    w "\"Thanks.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:920
translate english c02_0221:

    # c "가헬의 순수한 미소는 처음 보는 것 같다. 나는 마주 웃어주었다."
    c laugh "I've never seen such an innocent smile on Gahel's face. I smile back."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:927
translate english c02_0222:

    # "정말 다사다난했던 어제 이후로 평화로운 가게 영업을 하니 기분이 나른해졌다. 이틀 연속 휴업을 한 탓인지 손님도 몇 없어서 재료 손질에 시간을 쓸 수 있었다."
    "After yesterday's eventful day, the peaceful opening of the shop was a relaxing change of pace."
    
    "Since we were closed for two days in a row, we had very few customers, so I was able to spend some time preparing the ingredients."
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:929
translate english c02_0223:

    # "늘어지는 마음을 다잡기 위해 청소라도 하던 도중에 문이 열린다."
    "It was in the middle of cleaning as an effort to calm his nerves when the door opened."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:932
translate english c02_0224:

    # "{i}딸랑~{/i}"
    "{i}Chime~{/i}"
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:938
translate english c02_0225:

    # "상점에 들어온 건 흰색 곰이었다. 로브를 두르고 스태프를 든 모습이 전형적인 마법사의 복장이다. 익숙한 얼굴에 [pl_name][josa_eun_neun] 바로 인사를 건넸다."
    "A white bear entered the shop. He was dressed in robes and carrying a staff—a typical mage's attire. Seeing a familiar face, [pl_name] immediately rushed to greet him."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:940
translate english c02_0226:

    # c "\"어서 와. 한적할 때 잘 왔어.\""
    c talk "\"Welcome back. You've come at a good time.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:942
translate english c02_0227:

    # c "이 곰, 바토는 복장부터 알 수 있듯이 마법사다. 그것도 마탑의 정규 교육을 받은 엘리트 마법사."
    c base "This bear, Bato, is a mage, as one might surmise from his outfit. And not just any run-of-the-mill mage, but a formally trained elite mage of the Magic Tower."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:944
translate english c02_0228:

    # c "그를 처음 본다면 첫인상과 덩치에 조금 겁먹을 수 있지만 알고 보면 생각보다 말랑말랑한 곰이다."
    c "If one is seeing him for the first time, they might be a little intimidated by his size, but he's actually more cuddly than meets the eye."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:946
translate english c02_0229:

    # c "보기보다 수줍음도 많고 부끄럼도 타지만 마법 실력만큼은 일류라고 할 수 있다."
    c "He's more shy and reserved than he looks, but his magical proficiency is first-rate."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:952
translate english c02_0230:

    # b "\"안녕하세요, 형...\""
    b "\"Hey, big bro...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:958
translate english c02_0231:

    # c "그는 나보다 어리다. 마탑의 교육은 기사 수련과 달리 시험을 통과할 때까지 몇 년이고 계속되는데, 그 과정을 빠르게 졸업하고 벌써 몇 년째 실전에서 뛴다는 건 바토의 천재성을 증명하는 것이다."
    c "Bato is younger than me. Unlike a knight's training, tutelage at the Magic Tower persists years until the student passes the test."
    
    c "And it's a testament to Bato's ingenuity that he had graduated so quickly and already had years of field experience to his name."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:960
translate english c02_0232:

    # c "\"오늘은 무슨 일로 왔어?\""
    c talk "\"What brings you here today?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:967
translate english c02_0233:

    # b "\"그, 그게, 별건 아니고, 그냥... 확인하러 왔어요.\""
    b "\"It's, it's, it's not a big deal, I just... I just wanted to check in.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:974
translate english c02_0234:

    # c "\"음, 차라도 한 잔 내올게.\""
    c "\"Hm, I'll make you a cup of tea.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:976
translate english c02_0235:

    # c "바토가 말하는 '확인'은 여러 가지 의미가 있다. 이 가게가 멀쩡히 있는지, 나는 어디 잡혀가진 않았는지, 그리고 바토 본인의 상태까지 확인하러 온 것이다."
    c base "For Bato, 'checking in' means several things. He wants to make sure the store is okay, make sure that I am okay, and examine his condition as well."

# game/script/chapter2.rpy:978
translate english c02_0236:

    # c "그는 내 위험한 {color=#ee3939}'사업'{/color}에 대해 어느 정도 알고 있고 그것을 단속해야 하는 입장이지만, 동시에 나에게 목숨을 빚지고 나에게 협력하는 중이다."
    c "He has some knowledge of my dangerous {color=#ee3939}'business'{/color} and is in a position whose duty is to crack down on it, but at the same time, he owes me his life and is cooperating with me."

# game/script/chapter2.rpy:980
translate english c02_0237:

    # c "바토는 언제부턴가 심각한 {color=#ee3939}'마력 누수'{/color} 문제를 겪고 있다."
    c "Bato has been suffering from a serious case of {color=#ee3939}'mana leakage'{/color} for some time now."

# game/script/chapter2.rpy:982
translate english c02_0238:

    # c "마법을 사용할 때 마나가 조금 새는 정도는 흔한 일이지만, 바토는 평균 수준에 한참 못 미치는 효율이 나올 정도로 마나가 줄줄 새고 있었다."
    c "A little mana leaking out when using magic is not uncommon, but Bato was leaking mana to the point where his magic efficiency was well below average."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:984
translate english c02_0239:

    # c "출력이 약해지는 건 당연한 일, 남들과 같은 수준의 마법을 쓰려면 밑 빠진 독에 물을 붓는 것처럼 마나를 퍼부어야 한다. 그리고 그렇게 마력을 쓰다간 목숨이 위험해진다."
    c "A weaker magic output is only the start of the symptoms."
    
    c "Using magic at an output matching his peers was an act akin to pouring water into a cracked basin. And using mana like that could endanger his own life."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:993
translate english c02_0240:

    # b "\"여기 오면 왠지 마음이 편해요. 그렇게 자주 온 건 아니지만...\""
    b "\"There's something about coming here that makes me feel at ease, even though I don't come here that often...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:998
translate english c02_0241:

    # "바토는 차를 홀짝이며 우물쭈물 말했다. 생김새와 동떨어진 성격에는 왠지 그를 동생처럼 여기게 만드는 묘한 힘이 있다."
    "Bato sipped his tea and murmured. There's something about his appearance and personality that somehow makes me think of him as a younger brother."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1000
translate english c02_0242:

    # c "나는 바토를 가게 안쪽으로 이끌었다."
    c "I led Bato to the back of the store."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1002
translate english c02_0243:

    # c "\"잠깐 앉아볼래?\""
    c talk "\"Would you like to sit down for a minute?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1007
translate english c02_0244:

    # b "\"ㄴ, 네...\""
    b "\"Y, yes...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1014
translate english c02_0245:

    # c "나는 치유사가 진찰하는 것처럼 의자에 앉은 바토를 만졌다. 흰 털에 뒤덮인 살과 근육이 긴장한 듯 움찔거린다."
    c base "I touched Bato as he sat in the chair, as if I was a healer examining his health. Flesh and muscle covered in white fur twitched nervously."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1016
translate english c02_0246:

    # c "가헬이나 엘레드처럼 전문적인 훈련을 한 몸매는 아니어도 무시무시한 힘을 낼 수 있는 근육이 느껴진다."
    c "Even if he didn't have a professionally trained body like Gahel or Eled, you can feel that the muscles were capable of mustering fearsome power."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1018
translate english c02_0247:

    # c "흔해빠진 용병 나부랭이보단 바토가 더 주먹질을 잘할 것이다. 싸우는 모습을 내가 직접 보진 못했지만, 바토에게 맞고 곤죽이 된 암시장 상인의 얼굴은 본 적이 있다."
    c "Bato is probably better at throwing punches than the average mercenary. I've never seen him in a fight myself, but I've seen the face of a black market trader who was beaten to a pulp by a Bato."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1026
translate english c02_0248:

    # b "\"...힉!\""
    b "\"...Eek!\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1028
translate english c02_0249:

    # c "\"응? 왜 그래?\""
    c question2 "\"Huh? What's wrong?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1033
translate english c02_0250:

    # b "\"아, 아니, 아니에요.\""
    b "\"Oh no, no, it's nothing.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1035
translate english c02_0251:

    # c "아까보다 더 긴장했는지 바토의 털이 쭈뼛쭈뼛 서 있다. 폭신 말랑한 촉감이 중독적이라 더 만지고 싶지만 해야 할 일은 끝났으니 손을 뗐다."
    c base "'Bato's fur is standing on end, even tenser than before. The fluffy feeling is addictive, and I want to touch him more, but I realize the job was done."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1040
translate english c02_0252:

    # c "\"각인은 아무 문제 없어. 새어나간 마나도 잘 회수되고 있지?\""
    c talk "\"The imprinting is in good condition. The leaked mana is being recovered too, right?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1045
translate english c02_0253:

    # b "\"네. 고마워요, 형.\""
    b "\"Yep. Thanks a bunch, big bro.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1052
translate english c02_0254:

    # c "\"혹시 모르니 평소에 가장 자주 쓰는 마법 한번 써봐.\""
    c "\"Just in case, try your favorite spell.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1060
translate english c02_0255:

    # b "\"......\""
    b "\"......\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1062
translate english c02_0256:

    # "바토는 잠깐 고민하더니 들고 다니던 스태프의 마력 구체를 똑 뗐다."
    "Bato hesitated for a moment, then snapped off his staff's energy sphere."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1069
translate english c02_0257:

    # c "(저게 저렇게 떨어지는 물건이었구나...)"
    c base "(So he can even disassemble his staff like that…)"
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1071
translate english c02_0258:

    # "바토는 금속 재질처럼 보이는 구체에 손을 집어넣었다. 동그란 덩어리는 생김새와 다르게 액체처럼 물컹거리면서 바토의 손가락을 바로 집어삼켰다."
    "Bato stuck his hand into the sphere, which appeared to be made of metal. Despite its metallic appearance, the sphere fluctuated as if made of liquid as it wrapped around his fingers."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1079
translate english c02_0259:

    # "순식간에 형태를 변환하는 구체는 전투용 너클로 쓰는 것 같았다. 바토는 마력을 불어넣어 여러 종류의 강화 마법을 한 번에 사용했다."
    "It seemed Bato was using the sphere whose form can be altered instantaneously as combat knuckles. Bato energized it by casting several types of enhancement magic on it at once."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1087
translate english c02_0260:

    # b "\"... 멀쩡해요.\""
    b "\"…I'm good to go.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1105
translate english c02_0261:

    # "바토가 허공에 주먹질을 몇 번 하자 공기가 찢어지며 위협적인 바람 소리가 난다. 무시무시한 소리에 자연스럽게 [pl_name]의 털이 바짝 일어선다."
    "Bato pounds his fist into the air a few times, and a menacing whooshing noise reverberated as the air was sundered. The frightening sound makes [pl_name]'s fur stand on end."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1107
translate english c02_0262:

    # c "(저 정도면 한 방에 죽고도 남겠는데... 사람한테는 살살 하나 보다.)"
    c ddam2 "(That alone would be enough to kill me… So, he holds back against other people.)"
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1109
translate english c02_0263:

    # c "암시장 상인의 뭉개진 얼굴이 떠오르며 바토의 강함을 새삼 느꼈다."
    c base "The black market trader's crushed face flashed through my mind, reminding me of Bato's strength."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1111
translate english c02_0264:

    # c "육체적인 힘도 강하지만 그걸 보조해 주는 다양한 강화 마법들을 동시에 사용하는 것도 대단한 능력이다."
    c "His physical strength is impressive, but so is his ability to simultaneously use a variety of enhancement spells to support it."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1113
translate english c02_0265:

    # c "무기를 단단하게 만들고 육체를 빠르게 만들면서 받는 충격을 분산하는 완벽한 전투용 마법 조합이다."
    c "It's the perfect combination of combat magic, one that hardens his weapons and accelerates his movements while dispersing the impact of the strikes he takes."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1115
translate english c02_0266:

    # c "\"체감은 어때? 무리해서 마력을 쓰는 거 아냐?\""
    c talk "\"How does it feel? Aren't you using too much magic?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1123
translate english c02_0267:

    # "바토는 전투용 너클을 다시 스태프의 마력 구체로 돌려놓았다."
    "Bato returned the combat knuckles to its original state as the staff's magic sphere."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1131
translate english c02_0268:

    # b "\"괜찮아요. 이 정도면 160 도데카 정도...\""
    b "\"It's okay, It's only about 160 dodeca...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1144
translate english c02_0269:

    # c "\"160 도데카? 그게 뭐야?\""
    c question2 "\"160 dodeca? What is that?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1146
translate english c02_0270:

    # c "마탑의 교육을 받지 못한 나는 그 용어가 일종의 단위인 것은 눈치챘지만 정확한 의미는 알지 못했다. 바토는 내 반응을 보고 설명을 시작했다."
    c base "Having received no formal education at the Magic Tower, I only recognized that the term was a unit of measurement of some sort, but I didn't know what exactly it meant."
    
    c "Bato saw my reaction and began to explain."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1151
translate english c02_0271:

    # b "\"표준 마력 단위에요. 자주 쓰는 말은 아니고, 논문에서나 쓰는 거라...\""
    b "\"It's a standard unit of mana. It's a term you'd find more often in papers than regular conversation...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1153
translate english c02_0272:

    # b "\"마력의 12가지 발현 이론에서 생긴 용어인데, 아니 그게 중요한 게 아니지... 이건 기준점이 되는 표준 수정 구슬이 있으면 편한데.\""
    b "\"It's a term from the Theory of the 12 Manifestations of Magic, but no, that's not the point... I wish I had a crystal ball to use as a standard.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1155
translate english c02_0273:

    # b "\"아, 아예 직접 체감해 볼래요?\""
    b "\"Oh, do you want to try it out for yourself?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1162
translate english c02_0274:

    # "바토는 마법에 관련된 얘기라 그런지 평소보다 활기차게 말을 이었다. 그는 자연스럽게 [pl_name]의 손을 덥석 잡고는 미세한 마력을 흘려 넣었다."
    "Perhaps it was because the conversation was about magic, but Bato spoke with more vigor than usual. He casually grabbed [pl_name]'s hand and channeled a tiny bit of magic into it."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1165
translate english c02_0275:

    # c "(역시 손이 크네.)"
    c "(Those really are big hands.)"
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1172
translate english c02_0276:

    # b "\"이게 1 도데카에요. 아, 아닌가... 나는 두 배로 써야 정상으로 나오려나? 아무튼 아주 작은 단위라서 기초 마법도 5 도데카 이상은 쓰고 그래요.\""
    b "\"This is 1 dodeca. Oh, wait... Do I have to double it to get it to work? Anyway, it's a very small unit, so I'd have to spend at least 5 dodeca for basic magic.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1174
translate english c02_0277:

    # b "\"술식에 따라 다르지만 보통... 앗!\""
    b "\"It depends on the spell, but usually... Ah!\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1182
translate english c02_0278:

