    c "\"Yeah! Ah... Only the robe.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1481
translate english c02_0345:

    # "[pl_name][josa_eun_neun] 얼굴이 시뻘게진 바토를 의자 위에 앉게 했다."
    "[pl_name] sat Bato down on a chair, his expression bashful."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1483
translate english c02_0346:

    # "바토는 우물쭈물하다가 로브의 매듭을 풀었다."
    "Bato fumbled with the knot fastening his robes before untying them."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1490
translate english c02_0347:

    # c "로브를 벗자 드러난 바토의 몸은 묵직한 돌덩이 같았다. 목에 난 검은 갈기털 아래에는 대리석 같은 흰 털이 가득했다."
    c base "When his robes were removed, Bato's body was like a solid mass of stone. Beneath the black mane of hair on his neck, he was covered in fur as white as marble."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1492
translate english c02_0348:

    # c "바토의 어깨와 팔은 가헬이나 엘레드 못지않은 근육으로 울퉁불퉁했다."
    c "The musculature of Bato's shoulders and arms rivaled those of even Gahel's or Elred's."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1494
translate english c02_0349:

    # c "반면 가슴과 배는 동그랗고 말랑해 보인다. 바토는 벗은 로브를 가지런하게 정리해서 무릎 위에 올려놨다."
    c "His chest and stomach, on the other hand, look round and soft. Bato neatly folded the robe he shed and placed it on his lap."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1496
translate english c02_0350:

    # c "내가 바토의 뒤에 서서 등에 손을 대자, 바토는 흠칫 놀라며 숨을 들이켰다."
    c "When I stood behind him and put my hand on his back, he gasped in surprise."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1501
translate english c02_0351:

    # b "\"히익!...\""
    b "\"Hic!...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1503
translate english c02_0352:

    # c "(왜 내가 나쁜 짓을 하는 것 같지...)"
    c consider "(Why do I feel like I'm doing something vulgar...)"
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1508
translate english c02_0353:

    # c "커다란 덩치가 무색하게 바토는 곧 잡아먹힐 동물처럼 긴장했다. 바토의 넓은 등은 탄탄한 근육이 느껴지면서도 부드럽고 폭신했다."
    c base "Despite his size, Bato tensed like an animal about to be eaten. Bato's broad back was simultaneously hard with muscle and soft and fluffy."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1510
translate english c02_0354:

    # c "짧은 털의 촉감이 너무 좋아서 손을 뗄 수가 없다."
    c "I loved the feel of the short hairs and can't keep my hands off of them."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1512
translate english c02_0355:

    # c "마치 사람만큼 커다란 곰 인형을 쓰다듬고 있는 것 같았다. 뒤에서 보이는 동그란 귀가 왠지 귀엽게 느껴졌다."
    c "I felt like I was petting a teddy bear that was almost as big as me. The view of his rounded ears from the back was kind of cute."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1514
translate english c02_0356:

    # c "다른 곳의 감촉은 어떨까 궁금했지만, 나는 뒤늦게 정신을 차리고 말했다."
    c "I wondered what the feel would be like elsewhere, but then I came to my senses and began to speak."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1516
translate english c02_0357:

    # c "\"마력이 어떻게 새어 나오는지 측정해 볼게. 가벼운 마법 아무거나 써볼래?\""
    c talk "\"Let me measure how the mana leaks out. Can you cast any simple spell for me?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1521
translate english c02_0358:

    # "바토는 쭈뼛대다가 탐지 마법을 펼쳤다."
    "Bato twitched in nervousness before expanding a detection magic."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1531
translate english c02_0359:

    # "바토를 중심으로 바닥에 푸른 마법진이 생기더니 곧바로 마법진째 녹아내려 빛 덩어리가 되었다."
    "A blue magic circle appeared on the floor, centered on Bato, and quickly dissolved into a sphere of light."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1533
translate english c02_0360:

    # "그 빛은 순식간에 푸른 파도처럼 일렁이다가 방 밖으로 사라졌다."
    "The light flashed like a blue ocean waves for a split second before fading out of the room."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1535
translate english c02_0361:

    # "차원이 다른 사용법에 [pl_name]의 입이 딱 벌어졌지만, 지금은 집중해야 할 일이 있다."
    "While [pl_name]'s jaw dropped upon beholding such a high level of magic usage, he had work to focus on at the moment."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1537
translate english c02_0362:

    # c "\"음, 좌우로 퍼지는구나. 예상대로 금방 사라지네. 흠...\""
    c consider "\"Hmm, it's spreading left and right, and it's disappearing as quickly as I expected. Hmm...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1539
translate english c02_0363:

    # "결과를 머릿속에서 정리하는 동안 바토는 물끄러미 [pl_name][josa_eul_reul] 바라보았다."
    "Bato gazed at [pl_name] who was parsing through the results in his head."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1541
translate english c02_0364:

    # c "\"좋아. 어떻게 각인할지 떠올랐어.\""
    c talk "\"Okay, I've got an idea of how to engrave it.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1543
translate english c02_0365:

    # "[pl_name][josa_eun_neun] 창고에서 시술에 쓸 재료들을 가져왔다."
    "[pl_name] retrieved the ingredients for the procedure from the warehouse."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1545
translate english c02_0366:

    # "일반적인 문신과 다르게 마력 각인은 마나가 잘 통하는 재료를 쓰는 게 중요하다. 보석 가루, 연금용 정제수, 촉매로 쓸 마석과 액화 미스릴로 마법 잉크를 즉석 제조했다."
    "Unlike regular tattoos, mana imprinting requires mana-friendly materials. I improvised a magical ink from gemstone powder, alchemical water, gemstones that'll act a catalyst, and liquified Mithril."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1547
translate english c02_0367:

    # "방에서 기다리던 바토는 왠지 덩칫값 못하는 자세로 쭈그린 채 [pl_name][josa_i_ga] 재료들을 섞는 걸 구경했다."
    "Waiting in the room, Bato watched the [pl_name] ingredients being mixed, sulking in an fashion unbecoming of his immense size."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1552
translate english c02_0368:

    # b "\"잘, 부탁드려요...\""
    b "\"Take good care of me...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1557
translate english c02_0369:

    # c "나는 바토의 하얀 털 위에 그림 그리듯 잉크를 칠했다."
    c base "I inked over Bato's white fur in a painterly manner."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1562
translate english c02_0370:

    # c "손가락이 닿을 때마다 바짝 긴장한 바토가 움직이지 않으려고 하는 게 느껴진다."
    c "I can feel that the immensely jittery Bato was trying his best not to move with every touch of my fingers."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1564
translate english c02_0371:

    # c "사실 내가 하는 마법 시술은 보통의 마법진처럼 오차 없이 정교할 필요가 없다. 바토가 불쌍하니 최대한 빨리 끝내기로 했다."
    c "The truth is, my magical procedures didn't need to be as precise as the average magic circle. I felt sorry for Bato, so I decided to get it over with as quickly as possible."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1566
translate english c02_0372:

    # c "\"이제 마력으로 각인하면 끝!\""
    c talk "\"Now we just need to imprint it with magic power!\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1574
translate english c02_0373:

    # c "마력을 살포시 불어넣자, 마법 잉크는 바토의 몸속으로 사라졌다. 눈에 보이지 않지만, 존재는 확실히 느낄 수 있었다."
    c base "With a quick blast of energy, the magical ink disappeared into Bato's body. He couldn't see it, but he could feel it."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1576
translate english c02_0374:

    # c "\"어때?\""
    c talk "\"What do you think?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1591
translate english c02_0375:

    # c "바토는 다시 로브를 걸치고 손을 꼼지락거렸다. 몸에 술식이 새겨진 느낌은 좀 특이한 감각일 것이다."
    c base "Bato fidgeted with his hands in his robes again; it must be an odd sensation to have an imprinting in one's body."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1598
translate english c02_0376:

    # b "\"아... 이런 느낌이구나.\""
    b "\"Ah... So this is what it feels like.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1603
translate english c02_0377:

    # "바토는 손 위에 마력을 모았다가 거대한 마법진으로 변형시켰다. 마법진은 곧바로 사라졌으나 주변이 쥐 죽은 듯 고요해졌다."
    "Bato gathered the energy in his hands and transformed it into a massive magic circle. The circle quickly dissipated, but the area around it became eerily silent."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1622
translate english c02_0378:

    # c "\"뭐, 뭐야?\""
    c ddam2 "\"Wait, what?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1627
translate english c02_0379:

    # b "\"혹시 몰라서 결계를 쳤어요. 형... 형이 그 {color=#ee3939}'불법 시술'{/color}을 하는 사람이죠?\""
    b "\"I cast a barrier around the shop just in case. Big bro is... Uh, someone who performs {color=#ee3939}'illegal procedures'{/color}, right?\""

# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1632
translate english c02_0380:

    # c "정곡을 찔렸다. 하지만 나는 반사적으로 모른 체를 했다."
    c base "He hit the nail on the head. I reflexively pretended I didn't know what he was talking about."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1634
translate english c02_0381:

    # c "\"불법이라니, 방금 새긴 게 어떤 원리인지는 네가 더 잘 알텐데?\""
    c talk "\"What do you mean illegal? You should know better about how that thing I just carved functions, no?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1641
translate english c02_0382:

    # b "\"맞아요. 그래서 눈치챘어요. 술식은 전부 평범하지만, 근본적으로 이거 '마법'이 아니죠?\""
    b "\"Yeah, that’s why I noticed. The engravings are all ordinary, but fundamentally, they don’t count as 'magic', isn’t that so?\""

# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1646
translate english c02_0383:

    # c "두 번이나 비밀을 들켜서 심장이 철렁했다. 식은땀이 삐질삐질 나지만 최대한 뻔뻔하게 굴었다."
    c ddam "My heart sank at my secrets being uncovered not once but twice. I broke out in a cold sweat, but I tried to be as brazen as possible."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1648
translate english c02_0384:

    # c "\"그렇긴 한데, 딱히 금지된 것도 아니잖아? 그냥 마나를 쓰는 방법이 특이해서...\""
    c ddam2 "\"Yeah, but it's not really forbidden, right? It's just an unusual way to use mana...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1655
translate english c02_0385:

    # b "\"특이하긴 하죠. 마나를 제물로 {color=#ee3939}'주술'{/color}을 사용하는 사람이...\""
    b "\"Being unusual is one thing, and casting {color=#ee3939}'conjuration'{/color} by using mana as sacrifice is another...\""

# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1663
translate english c02_0386:

    # c "결국 나는 말문이 막혔다. 대체 어디까지 알고 있는 거지?"
    c consider "Eventually I was left speechless. Just how much does he know?"
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1665
translate english c02_0387:

    # c "내가 스승님에게 배운 것은 마법뿐만이 아니라 {color=#ee3939}'주술'{/color}도 있었다. 주술은 마법 이전부터 존재하던 고대의 기술로, 이제는 사용할 줄 아는 사람이 거의 없다."
    c base "What I learned from my master was not only magic, but {color=#ee3939}'conjuration'{/color}. Conjurations are an ancient art that predates magic, and very few people today know how to wield it."

# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1667
translate english c02_0388:

    # c "제물을 사용하면 강력한 효과를 얻을 수 있기에, 나는 중요한 일에 주술을 이용하곤 했다."
    c "Since sacrifices have powerful effects, I used conjurations when the occasional called for it."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1670
translate english c02_0389:

    # b "\"그리고 방금 탐지 마법으로 마을 밖에 궤짝을 놓고 온 것도 알아냈어요. 내용물까진 모르겠지만... 들키면 안 되니 숨긴 거죠?\""
    b "\"And I just found out that you left a chest outside the village with the detection spell. I don't know what's in it, but... You hid it because you didn't want to be found, right?\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1673
translate english c02_0390:

    # c "(헉!!)"
    c ddam2 "(Huh!!)"
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1675
translate english c02_0391:

    # c "식은땀이 아니라 진땀이 줄줄 흘렀다. 숨겨놓은 특제 회복 물약까지 들키면 정말로 끝장이다."
    c ddam "What trickled down my back was no longer drops cold sweat but a waterfall of it. Now if he finds out about my stash of special healing potions, it really was curtains for me."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1677
translate english c02_0392:

    # c "꼬리가 길면 밟힌다더니 결국 마탑에 잡혀가는구나... 눈앞이 캄캄해지고 다리에 힘이 풀려 쓰러질 것 같았다."
    c "What was the saying, that if one has a long tail, it will get stepped on? I felt like I was going to collapse as my eyes went dark and my legs weakened."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1683
translate english c02_0393:

    # c "갑자기 바토가 내 손을 덥석 잡아서 이대로 즉시 연행되는 건가 생각했다."
    c "Suddenly, Bato grabbed my hand, and I thought I was going to be taken away immediately."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1694
translate english c02_0394:

    # b "\"차라리 형이라서 다행이에요. 어차피 한 배를 탄 사이니까, 마탑에는 비밀로 할게요.\""
    b "\"I'm glad you're my big brother. We're in the same boat, and I won't tell anyone about it.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1699
translate english c02_0395:

    # c "전혀 예상하지 못한 말에 나는 얼빠진 대답을 했다."
    c base "After hearing the unexpected response, I blurted out."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1701
translate english c02_0396:

    # c "\"어? 그, 그래...\""
    c talk "\"Huh? W… Well yeah...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1709
translate english c02_0397:

    # b "\"너무 걱정하지 마요. 마탑 측에서 이런 일을 추적하는 건 저밖에 없으니까.\""
    b "\"Don't worry about it, I'm the only one whose job is to keep tabs on stuff at the Magic Tower.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1714
translate english c02_0398:

    # c "\"고생이 많네...\""
    c "\"That's a lot of work...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1716
translate english c02_0399:

    # c "나는 아무 말이나 반사적으로 내뱉었다. 짧은 시간에 너무 많은 감정이 휘몰아쳐서 오히려 멍청해진 기분이었다."
    c base "I reflexively blurted out the words. So many emotions rushed through me in such a short time that I felt rather stupid."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1718
translate english c02_0400:

    # c "나는 혼이 쏙 빠진 채로 멍하니 있다가 바토가 꽉 쥔 손이 저려서 정신을 차렸다."
    c "I stood there dumbfounded, until I felt my hands go sore within Bato's grip and came to my senses."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1720
translate english c02_0401:

    # c "\"아, 고마워. 정말, 어떻게 되는 줄 알았어...\""
    c talk "\"Oh, thanks. Really, I thought I was a goner...\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1725
translate english c02_0402:

    # b "\"그건 제가 할 말이에요. 형은 목숨의 은인이나 마찬가지인걸요.\""
    b "\"That's for me to say. You might as well have saved my life.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1732
translate english c02_0403:

    # c "바토는 또다시 동생 같은 눈빛으로 나를 바라보았다. 정신 조작 계열 마법이 아닌가 의심될 정도로 강력한 귀여움에 나는 결국 패배했다."
    c base "Bato peered at me again, this time with the gaze of a younger brother. I was defeated by a cuteness so powerful that I suspected it was a type of mind manipulation magic."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1734
translate english c02_0404:

    # c "자연스럽게 바토의 머리를 쓰다듬고 나서야 풀려날 수 있었다. 오늘 처음 만난 사이에 좀 과한 스킨쉽 아닌가 싶지만 아무렴 어때."
    c happy "Naturally, I stroked Bato's head before I was released from his grip. I think it was a little too much skin-to-skin contact for someone I just met today, but whatever."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1741
translate english c02_0405:

    # b "\"그럼... 다음에 또 올게요.\""
    b "\"Well... I'll come back another time.\""
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1743
translate english c02_0406:

    # "바토는 행복한 미소를 지으며 돌아갔다."
    "Bato walked away with a happy smile on his face."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1747
translate english c02_0407:

    # c "그렇게 바토와 만난 첫날은 폭풍과 같이 지나갔다. 그 뒤로 바토는 가끔씩 가게에 찾아와서 각인을 점검받거나 소소한 수다를 떨거나 했다."
    c base "That first day with Bato went by tempestuously, and since then, he's stopped by the shop occasionally to have his engravings checked and to make small talk."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1749
translate english c02_0408:

    # c "처음엔 혹시 나를 방심시키려는 계획이 아닐까 했는데, 바토는 정말로 나를 동료나 친구로 생각하는 것 같았다."
    c "At first, I thought he was just trying to catch me off guard, but he seemed to genuinely consider me a colleague or friend."
 
 
# game/script/chapter2.rpy:1751
